TASKS:  
============
1. Fetch Training data  
    a. Fetch happy tweets
        This fetches tweets based on happy filter.
    b. Fetch sad tweets
        This fetches sad tweets based on sad filter.
2. Train Classifier
    It uses happy and sad tweets and creates index which is then used for 
    classifying incomming data.
3. Start Classifying input
    Fetches tweets. Each tweet is classified using two filters. 
        a. Other classifies it based on location. 
        b. One filter classifies it based on sad or happy index.

TECHNOLOGY:
=============
1. Written in Python
2. Uses Redis for storage
3. Persistant data is stored in MongoDB
